00:15:13,212 --> 00:15:14,736
so he studied human anatomy

248
00:15:14,914 --> 00:15:18,247
and how to strengthen
his own body through exercising.

249
00:15:19,351 --> 00:15:22,787
Though for a while, only dancers
were interested in the method,

250
00:15:23,489 --> 00:15:26,617
Pilates had already started his
work as a skilled technician

251
00:15:26,792 --> 00:15:29,317
in physical rehabilitation.

252
00:15:29,695 --> 00:15:31,287
Joseph Pilates.

253
00:15:32,965 --> 00:15:34,489
It's him? Is he alive?

254
00:15:34,667 --> 00:15:36,726
No, he died. He worked...

255
00:15:36,902 --> 00:15:38,699
- Four eyes.
