without warning.

436
00:28:49,160 --> 00:28:51,321
But that's normal, right?

437
00:28:51,496 --> 00:28:52,827
- But of course.
- There's no hurry.

438
00:28:53,164 --> 00:28:54,654
It's normal.

439
00:28:54,833 --> 00:28:57,324
We try to make them feel
it's normal.

440
00:28:57,502 --> 00:28:59,094
Sometimes
they feel embarrassed.

441
