the party on the bulletin board.

444
00:29:08,613 --> 00:29:11,104
- Not really.
- We are preparing a play,

445
00:29:11,282 --> 00:29:13,807
to get to know each other better,
through theater,

446
00:29:14,152 --> 00:29:16,712
so all the daddies can participate.

447
00:29:17,255 --> 00:29:20,053
No, I'm very shy.
I can't do it.

448
00:29:20,225 --> 00:29:22,455
- We'll all participate.
-Anyway, I think it's great....

449
00:29:22,627 --> 00:29:26,393
- We’ll all dress-up as buffoons.
- No, I won't do it.

450
00:29:26,564 --> 00:29:27,826
But it's very important.

451
00:29:28,166 --> 00:29:31,363
Like I sold, I think it's great
they do things Like that, but...

452
00:29:31,536 --> 00:29:33,094
But all the dads plan to take part.

453
00:29:33,271 --> 00:29:35,796
There he is!
Hernan, our counselor.

454
00:29:36,174 --> 00:29:37,607
You're Gaston's father, right?

455
00:29:37,776 --> 00:29:39,300
The twins' parents are downstairs?

456
00:29:39,477 --> 00:29:41,377
Yes, I’ll be right with them.

457
00:29:41,546 --> 00:29:42,774
- Good bye.
- See you Later.

458
00:29:43,481 --> 00:29:45,210
Hernan's a professional.

459
00:29:45,383 --> 00:29:50,480
He could help you
with your communication problem...

460
00:29:51,322 --> 00:29:53,256
What communication problems?

461
00:29:53,458 --> 00:29:57,224
...and in that way,
they had lots of energy.

462
00:29:57,662 --> 00:29:59,596
- Hello.
