488
00:31:11,636 --> 00:31:12,830
No, not yet.

489
00:31:13,004 --> 00:31:14,437
Come to Astorga's diner.

490
00:31:14,606 --> 00:31:17,336
Not the one on Florida,
they closed it down.

491
00:31:17,508 --> 00:31:19,669
Today?
I have a thousand things...

492
00:31:19,844 --> 00:31:21,812
Take a cab, I’ll pay for it.

493
00:31:21,980 --> 00:31:24,915
I don't need you to pay for it.
